            <img src="https://www.maxroser.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/maxroser_rosermax01_square-smaller-file-size.png"/>
            <div>
                <h4>Max Roser</h4>
                <span>- Project Director</span>
                <p>Max is an economist at the University of Oxford and the founder of Our World in Data. He began the project in 2011 and for several years was the sole author, until receiving funding for the formation of a team. Max's research focuses on poverty, health, and the distribution of incomes. He has a background in economics, geoscience and philosophy.</p>
                <a href="mailto:max@ourworldindata.org">max@ourworldindata.org</a> / <a href="http://twitter.com/MaxCRoser">@MaxCRoser</a>
            </div>
